high_descs: pick up the butter knife with the yellow handle
put the knife in the left side of the sink and then pick back up
return knife to counter where it was
anns.task_desc: get a yellow knife, put it in the sink then return it to it's spot

high_descs: Turn around, go to sink, turn right to face sink.
Pick up the left knife off of the sink ledge.
Move to the second sink on the left by turning left and right.
Place knife in left sink, to the right of the potato and drain.  Turn the water on then off, drain the water.  Pick the knife up.
Turn around and face the sink.
Place the knife on the left sink ledge.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife with a yellow handle on the edge of the sink.
Step to the left to face the left side of the sink.
Wash the knife with a yellow handle in the left side of the sink and pick it back up.
Step back and face the left side of the sink.
Place the knife with a yellow handle in it's original spot on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To clean a knife and put it back in its spot on the edge of the left side of the sink.
